                    <i class="fas fa-lock feature-icon"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-content">
                    <p class="textleft"><b>Different access levels</b></p>
                    <p class="textleft">Create separate dashboards, views, and actions for inventory managers and sales managers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="feature-box">
                <div class="feature-icon-container">
                    <i class="fas fa-box-open feature-icon"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-content">
                    <p class="textleft"><b>Inventory management</b></p>
                    <p class="textleft">Show a table listing of products with images, including name, current stock count, and units sold.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">        
            <div class="feature-box">
                <div class="feature-icon-container">
                    <i class="fas fa-truck feature-icon"></i>
