                    <p class="textleft">Create new purchase and sales orders from directly within the app, and keep track of order status.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="feature-box">
                <div class="feature-icon-container">
                    <i class="fas fa-search feature-icon"></i>
                </div>
